啦"},{"pid":"f50d5e49959a65975e5f220ecb9cccc2b8c47a5b","tid":1252074,"uid":242630,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:53:59.000Z","msg":"要收尻呢條爛坦皮，靠兄弟發達，你老母大是大非面對企人民幣個邊"},{"pid":"d3713c0f38eb19285d8a1b4188efcad363c79476","tid":1252074,"uid":186905,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:54:45.000Z","msg":"他坦言商業化後就會變質，所以沒有這個想法。"},{"pid":"d45b5f0f1d5fda421f1dc385418cf6be4bd41f64","tid":1252074,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:14:57.000Z","msg":"可以幾肯定達哥唔會因為你哋連登仔而收皮<br />\n<br />\n正如慕容公子咁一樣大把人支持<br />\n<br />\n何況正值人氣高峰期嘅達哥"},{"pid":"10bad73f0b85c189a97ca44e64136ae87655dc92","tid":1252074,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:06:08.000Z","msg":"鳩估當日會有六七千人睇佢同圍插佢加埋世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18c0f83a159c2f6e1f4e92fc097c58ff8a82aff","tid":1252074,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:08:15.000Z","msg":"覺得依家既達哥變左質<br />\n以前既達哥去左邊"},{"pid":"dfa617f2a2ede11c007dea85dae0a411e53a5973","tid":1252074,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f50d5e49959a65975e5f220ecb9cccc2b8c47a5b","tid":1252074,"uid":242630,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:53:59.000Z","msg":"要收尻呢條爛坦皮，靠兄弟發達，你老母大是大非面對企人民幣個邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:10:46.000Z","msg":"妖，叫得「達哥」都唔慌好嘢，嗰個「蝗鳩達」都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79aec4d3e38aa9a5af20c7e8b66048c22e44f6e","tid":1252074,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f18c0f83a159c2f6e1f4e92fc097c58ff8a82aff","tid":1252074,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:08:15.000Z","msg":"覺得依家既達哥變左質<br />\n以前既達哥去左邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"去咗你哋心裡面"}]}